  <p>CADU has a highly experienced management team in the Mexican housing development industry, with proven expertise and performance in the subprime crises and the most recent housing crisis in Mexico. The Company ascribes a large portion of its operational and financial success to its management team.</p>

  <p>The management team of CADU and its Subsidiaries is composed of top-level executives, including CADU´s current shareholders, which provides great flexibility to the Company, streamlining the decision-making process and its respective execution.</p>
